<refentry id="function.getdate">
 <refnamediv>
  <refname>getdate</refname>
  <refpurpose>Obtiene informaci&oacute;n de fecha/hora</refpurpose>
 </refnamediv>
 <refsect1>
  <title>Descripci&oacute;n</title>
  <methodsynopsis>
   <type>array</type><methodname>getdate</methodname>
   <methodparam choice="opt"><type>int</type><parameter>marca_de_tiempo</parameter></methodparam>
  </methodsynopsis>
  <para>
   Devuelve un valor <type>array</type> asociativo que contiene
   informaci&oacute;n de fecha sobre la
   <parameter>marca_de_tiempo</parameter>, o la hora local actual si
   no se entrega una <parameter>marca_de_tiempo</parameter>, con los
   siguientes elementos en la matriz asociativa:
  </para>
  <para>
   <table>
    <title>Elementos clave de la matriz asociativa devuelta</title>
    <tgroup cols="3">
     <thead>
      <row>
       <entry>Clave</entry>
       <entry>Descripci&oacute;n</entry>
       <entry>Ejemplo de valores devueltos</entry>
      </row>
     </thead>
     <tbody>
      <row>
       <entry><literal>"seconds"</literal></entry>
       <entry>Representaci&oacute;n num&eacute;rica de
       segundos</entry>
       <entry><literal>0</literal> a <literal>59</literal></entry>
      </row>
      <row>
       <entry><literal>"minutes"</literal></entry>
       <entry>Representaci&oacute;n num&eacute;rica de minutos</entry>
       <entry><literal>0</literal> a <literal>59</literal></entry>
      </row>
      <row>
       <entry><literal>"hours"</literal></entry>
       <entry>Representaci&oacute;n num&eacute;rica de horas</entry>
       <entry><literal>0</literal> a <literal>23</literal></entry>
      </row>
      <row>
       <entry><literal>"mday"</literal></entry>
       <entry>Representaci&oacute;n num&eacute;rica del d&iacute;a del
       mes</entry>
       <entry><literal>1</literal> a <literal>31</literal></entry>
      </row>
      <row>
       <entry><literal>"wday"</literal></entry>
       <entry>Representaci&oacute;n num&eacute;rica del d&iacute;a de
       la semana</entry>
       <entry><literal>0</literal> (para el Domingo) a
       <literal>6</literal> (para el S&aacute;bado)</entry>
      </row>
      <row>
       <entry><literal>"mon"</literal></entry>
       <entry>Representaci&oacute;n num&eacute;rica de un mes</entry>
       <entry><literal>1</literal> a <literal>12</literal></entry>
      </row>
      <row>
       <entry><literal>"year"</literal></entry>
       <entry>Una representaci&oacute;n num&eacute;rica completa de un
       a&ntilde;o, 4 d&iacute;gitos</entry>
       <entry>Ejemplos: <literal>1999</literal> o
       <literal>2003</literal></entry>
      </row>
      <row>
       <entry><literal>"yday"</literal></entry>
       <entry>Representaci&oacute;n num&eacute;rica del d&iacute;a del
       a&ntilde;o</entry>
       <entry><literal>0</literal> a <literal>365</literal></entry>
      </row>
      <row>
       <entry><literal>"weekday"</literal></entry>
       <entry>Una representaci&oacute;n textual completa del
       d&iacute;a de la semana</entry>
       <entry><literal>Sunday</literal> a <literal>Saturday</literal></entry>
      </row>
      <row>
       <entry><literal>"month"</literal></entry>
       <entry>Una representaci&oacute;n textual completa de un mes,
       como January o March</entry>
       <entry><literal>January</literal> a <literal>December</literal></entry>
      </row>
      <row>
       <entry><literal>0</literal></entry>
       <entry>
        Segundos desde el Epoch Unix, similar a los valores devueltos
        por <function>time</function> y usados por
        <function>date</function>.
       </entry>
       <entry>
        Depende del sistema, t&iacute;picamente
        <literal>-2147483648</literal> a
        <literal>2147483647</literal>.
       </entry>
      </row>
     </tbody>
    </tgroup>
   </table>
  </para>
  <para>
   <example>
    <title>Ejemplo de <function>getdate</function></title>
    <programlisting role="php">
<![CDATA[
<?php
$hoy = getdate();
print_r($hoy);
?>
]]>
    </programlisting>
    &example.outputs.similar;
    <screen>
<![CDATA[
Array
(
    [seconds] => 40
    [minutes] => 58
    [hours]   => 21
    [mday]    => 17
    [wday]    => 2
    [mon]     => 6
    [year]    => 2003
    [yday]    => 167
    [weekday] => Tuesday
    [month]   => June
    [0]       => 1055901520
)
]]>
    </screen>
   </example>
  </para>
  <para>
   Vea tambi&eacute;n <function>date</function>,
   <function>time</function>, y <function>setlocale</function>.
  </para>
 </refsect1>
</refentry>

